Introduction

LUN8wave (Korean: 루네이트웨이브; Japanese: ルネイトウェーブ) is a sub-unit from the boy group LUN8 formed by Fantagio Entertainment. LUN8wave will make their debut on November 22nd, 2023, with the single '‘여기 붙어라 (Playground)".
